// Messages started with two forwardslashes are comments and are ignored by the interpreter.
// Clear the console of file loading messages.
clear

// Ask the user how many repetitions they want
write("Input repetitions: "),
// Recieve an integer input from the user
input int(reps)

// Greet the console given amount of times.
repeat(&reps):
>write("Hello!")

// An end statement is added to prevent crashing and for good practise.
end